gt.blockmachines.extremeheatexchanger.tooltip=Machine Type: §eHeat Exchanger, EHE§r\nInputs are §cLava§7, §cHot Coolant§7, §cHot Solar Salt§7, or §cPlasma\nOutputs are §9Pahoehoe Lava§7, §9IC2 Coolant§7, §9Cold Solar Salt§7, or §9Molten Metal\nConverts distilled water into §rSH Steam§7 or §rSC Steam§7 in the process\nOutputs §rSC Steam§7 if the input rate of hot fluid is above a certain §dthreshold\nExplodes immediately if it runs out of distilled water\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§cLava§7 | SC Threshold §d80,000 mB/s§7 | Max Input §c160,000 mB/s§7 | Max Output §r640,000 mB/t SC Steam\n§cHot Coolant§7 | SC Threshold §d8,000 mB/s§7 | Max Input §c16,000 mB/s§7 | Max Output §r160,000 mB/t SC Steam\n§cHot Solar Salt§7 | SC Threshold §d1,600 mB/s§7 | Max Input §c3,200 mB/s§7 | Max Output §r160,000 mB/t SC Steam\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§cPlasma§7 always outputs §rDense SC Steam§7 regardless of input rate\nThe max input and output rates depend on the plasma's density (EU/L)\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nA circuit in the controller lowers the SC threshold at the cost of steam\n§d-1.5%§7 SC Threshold and §r-1.5%§7 steam output per circuit over 1\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
