gt.blockmachines.megablastfurnace.tooltip=Machine Type: §eBlast Furnace, MEBF, MBF§r\n§4DEPRECATED - Controller will be removed in next major update!\n§4Check NEI for new Controller and conversion recipe\n§6256§7 Parallels\n§b-5%§7 EU Usage per §c900K§7 above the recipe requirement\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nIncreases Heat by §c100K§7 for every §fVoltage§7 tier past §bMV\nEvery §c1800K§7 over the recipe requirement grants 1 §dPerfect Overclock\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§2§nUV§7-tier §fGlass§7 required for §9Tec§1Tech§7 Laser Hatches\nEnergy Hatch limited by §fGlass§7 Tier, §c§l§nUMV§7-tier unlocks all\nThis machine can run recipes regardless of tier, if given enough energy\n§5102400 §7Pollution per second\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
gt.blockmachines.megablastfurnace.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §615§7x§620§7x§615§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center, 3rd layer\n§6   0x§7 - §6447x §r§7Heat Proof Machine Casing\n§6   864x §r§7Heating Coil (tiered)\n§6   1007x §r§7Any Tiered Glass (tiered)\n   The glass tier limits the Energy Input tier\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any bottom layer Casing\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any bottom layer Casing\n§f   Muffler Hatch: §7Top middle\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any bottom layer Casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any bottom layer Casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any bottom layer Casing\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any Heat Proof Machine Casing\n   Uses sub channel §6glass§r§7 for §6Glass Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6coil§r§7 for §6Heating Coil Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
