gt.blockmachines.multi.bec.diode.tooltip=Machine Type: §eBEC Diode, Storage Bus§r\n§7§b§lMaxwell's Demon's Big Brother§b§7\n§7Controls the flow of condensate in the network.\n§7Condensate that is present in the left hatch's network will be exposed to the right hatch's network.\n§7The opposite is not true; condensate can only flow in one direction.\n§7A §6Bose-Einstein Condensate Entanglement Apparatus§6§7 can only push condensate from the right hatch into the left hatch.\n§7Using a §6Machine Controller Cover§6§7 on the controller will enable or disable transfers.\n§7Consumes §a1A UIV§7 while active, regardless of the network's status.\n§7§8§m-----------------------------------------§8§7\n§7Condensate can be filtered in the parameters window.\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nAdded by: §a§9Recursive Pineapple§r§7
