gt.blockmachines.multimachine.cracker.name=Oil Cracking Unit
gt.blockmachines.multimachine.cracker.tooltip=Machine Type: §eCracker, OCU§r\n§b-10%§7 EU Usage per §fHeating Coil§7 Tier\nMaximum of §b50%§7 EU discount\nThermally cracks heavy hydrocarbons into lighter fractions\nMore efficient than the Chemical Reactor\nGives different benefits whether it hydro or steam-cracks:\nHydro - Consumes 20% less Hydrogen and outputs 25% more cracked fluid\nSteam - Outputs 50% more cracked fluid\n(Values compared to cracking in the Chemical Reactor)\nPlace the appropriate circuit in the controller or an input bus\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
