gt.blockmachines.multimachine.entropic-processor.name=Entropic Processor
gt.blockmachines.multimachine.entropic-processor.tooltip=Machine Type: §eEntropic Processor§r\nProcesses substances by increasing or decreasing their entropy\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHas §68§7 parallels by default\nUsing Advanced Alchemical Constructs increases the machine's parallels to §632§7\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nMixes fluids or solids with a magical catalyst\nCatalyst is consumed by the recipe, then returned upon completion\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nPerforms one perfect overclock per casing tier (Thaumium = 1 perfect OC)\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
gt.blockmachines.multimachine.entropic-processor.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §67§7x§65§7x§67§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center\n§6   24x §r§7Warded Glass\n§6   65x§7 - §697x §r§7Alchemically Resistant/Inert/Immune Casing (tiered)\n§6   3x §r§7Alchemical Construct (tiered)\n§f   Maintenance Hatch: §7Any Alchemically Resistant/Inert/Immune Casing (Hint: 1)\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any Alchemically Resistant/Inert/Immune Casing (Hint: 1)\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Alchemically Resistant/Inert/Immune Casing (Hint: 1)\n§f   Output Hatch: §7Any Alchemically Resistant/Inert/Immune Casing (Hint: 1)\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any Alchemically Resistant/Inert/Immune Casing (Hint: 1)\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any Alchemically Resistant/Inert/Immune Casing (Hint: 1)\n   Uses sub channel §6casing§r§7 for §6Alchemical Casing Tier\n   Uses sub channel §6construct§r§7 for §6Alchemical Construct Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
gt.blockmachines.multimachine.exofoundry.name=Exo-Foundry
gt.blockmachines.multimachine.exofoundry.tooltip=Machine Type: §eFluid Solidifier§r\n§616§7 Parallels per §fVoltage§7 Tier\n§a150%§7 Speed\n§8100%§7 EU Usage\nWill §lnot§7 perform §doverclocks§7 over the hatch tier without modules\nWill §lnot§7 process §1§nUIV+§7 voltage tier recipes without modules\nHas §63 Tiers§7, depending on Central Chassis Casing\nHas §62/3/4§7 Module Slots, based on machine tier\nEach Module Slot has §67§7 different options\n§6Modules§7 are selected inside the Controller\n§6Module§7 stats are shown in NEI and the Controller\nToggle Render with Screwdriver\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§cGlorious Evolution!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
gt.blockmachines.multimachine.exofoundry.tooltip_secondary=§fDimensions: §615§7x§655§7x§615§7 (§6W§7x§6H§7x§6L§7) §c(Hollow)\n§fStructure: \n   §fController: §7Front center, 2nd layer\n§6   462x §r§7Primary Exo-Foundry Casing (minimum)\n§6   548x §r§7Exo-Foundry Containment Glass\n§6   282x §r§7Inner Foundry Siphon Casing\n§6   260x §r§7Central Magnetic Chassis (tiered)\n§6   224x §r§7Netherite Frame Box\n§6   196x §r§7Central Exo-Foundry Regulation Casing\n§6   173x §r§7Black Plutonium Item Pipe Casing\n§f   Input Bus: §7Any Foundry Casing\n§f   Output Bus: §7Any Foundry Casing\n§f   Input Hatch: §7Any Foundry Casing\n§f   Energy Hatch: §7Any Foundry Casing\n   Uses sub channel §6chassis§r§7 for §6Magnetic Chassis Tier\n   §7§m------------------------------\n   Check NEI for Module structure costs\n   §7§m------------------------------\n§fTo see the structure, use a§9 Structure§1Lib §r§fHologram Projector on the Controller!
gt.blockmachines.multimachine.exothermichearth.name=Exothermic Hearth
gt.blockmachines.multimachine.exothermichearth.tooltip=Machine Type: §eBlast Furnace, ExH, MEBF, MBF§r\n§6256§7 Parallels\n§b-5%§7 EU Usage per §c900K§7 above the recipe requirement\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nIncreases Heat by §c100K§7 for every §fVoltage§7 tier past §bMV\nEvery §c1800K§7 over the recipe requirement grants 1 §dPerfect Overclock\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nWhile active, the machine will heat up and multiply its parallels up to §62x\nTakes §d30 minutes§7 of constant running to reach maximum multiplier\nWhile not running, the machine will rapidly cooldown\nOptionally supply §c250 mB§7/s of §6Pyrotheum§7 to speed up heating by §c6x\nThe drain rate of §6Pyrotheum§7 will increase §dlinearly§7 with the parallel multiplier\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\n§2§nUV§7-tier §fGlass§7 required for §9Tec§1Tech§7 Laser Hatches\nEnergy Hatch limited by §fGlass§7 Tier, §c§l§nUMV§7-tier unlocks all\nThis machine can run recipes regardless of tier, if given enough energy\n§5102400 §7Pollution per second\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§o§4Never one...\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nStructure by: §aGregTech Odyssey§r§7
