gt.blockmachines.multimachine.extremedieselengine.tooltip=Machine Type: §eCombustion Generator, ECE§r\n§4DEPRECATED - Controller will be removed in next major update!\n§4Check NEI for new Controller and conversion recipe\nSupply high rating fuel and 8000L of Lubricant per hour to run\nSupply 40L/s of Liquid Oxygen to boost output (optional)\nDefault: Produces 10900EU/t at 100% fuel efficiency\nBoosted: Produces 32700EU/t at 150% fuel efficiency\nYou need to wait for it to reach 300% to output full power\n§53840 §7Pollution per second\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
