gt.blockmachines.multimachine.extremegreenhouse.name=Extreme Industrial Greenhouse
gt.blockmachines.multimachine.extremegreenhouse.tooltip=Machine Type: §eCrop Farm, EIG§r\nGrow your crops like a chad!\nUse screwdriver to enable/change/disable setup mode\nUse screwdriver while sneaking to enable/disable IC2 mode\nUse wire cutters to give incoming IC2 seeds 0 humidity\nUses 1000L of water per seed per operation\nUses 1L of Weed-EX 9000 per operation per seed if it contains more than 1000 seeds\nOtherwise, around 1% of seeds will be voided each operation\nYou can insert fertilizer each operation to get more drops (max + 400)\nEnergy Hatch limited by §fGlass§7 Tier\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§6Setup Mode:\nDoes not take power\nThere are two modes: input / output\nInput mode: machine will take seeds from input bus and plant them\n[IC2] You need to also input block that is required under the crop\nOutput mode: machine will take planted seeds and output them\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§6Normal Crops:\nMinimal voltage tier: §8EV§7\nStarting with 1 slot\nEvery tier past §8EV§7, slots are multiplied by 2\nEvery slot adds 64 seed to the total seed capacity\nBase process time: 5 sec\nProcess time is divided by number of tiers past §eHV§7 (Minimum 1 sec)\nAll crops are grown at the end of the operation\nDoes not drop seeds\nCan consume up to 2 fertilizer per seed per cycle\nBoost per fertilizer: 200%\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§cDEPRECATED§r\n§6IC2 Crops:\nMinimal voltage tier: §dLuV§7\nMinimal glass tier: §dLuV§7\nStarting with 4 slot\nEvery tier past §dLuV§7, slots are multiplied by 4\nEvery slot adds 1 seed to the total seed capacity\nProcess time: 5 sec\nAll crops are accelerated by x32 times\nCan consume up to 40 fertilizer per seed per cycle\nBoost per fertilizer: 10%\nWeed-EX 9000 consumption is multiplied by 5\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nAdded by: §a§4§lk§c§lu§6§lb§e§la§2§l6§a§l0§b§l0§3§l0§r§7\nStructure by: §aHydroCN§r§7
