gt.blockmachines.multimachine.mega_distillation_tower.tooltip=Machine Type: §eDistillery, DT, MDT§r\nStats dictated by tower mode, change mode in GUI or with a screwdriver\nHas up to 5 middle slices and 1 top slice, the amount of middle slices is the 'Tower Height'\nEach middle slice adds 2 output hatches, the top slice adds one output hatch\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nDistillery Mode\n§6256 * (1 + Tower Height/2)§7 Parallels\n§a150%§7 Speed\n§b50%§7 EU Usage\nFluids output to the first hatch only\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nDistillation Tower Mode\n§6256§7 Parallels\n§a120%§7 Speed\n§b90%§7 EU Usage\nFluids output to their corresponding layer only\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\nThis machine can run recipes regardless of tier, if given enough energy\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§6Big Oil will be pleased with this!\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nStructure by: §a§6Mallady§r§7
