gt.blockmachines.multimachine.nanochipmodule.assemblymatrix.name=Nanochip Assembly Matrix
gt.blockmachines.multimachine.nanochipmodule.assemblymatrix.tooltip=Machine Type: §eAssembly Matrix, NAC Module§r\nModule of the §aNanochip Assembly Complex§7\nAssembles your Circuits §eCCs§7 with Component §eCCs§7\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nMaximum allowed recipe tier is determined by §fComponent Assembly Line Casing§7 Tier\nOverclocks recipes (Energy Hatch Tier - Recipe Casing Tier) times\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§d§oAfter processing your CCs through an intricate pipeline, they are finally§7\n§d§oready to be assembled into a circuit. This circuit can be converted into a real§7\n§d§oitem in the NAC control center, or processed further into a higher tier circuit§7\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
