gt.blockmachines.multimachine.nanochipmodule.boadprocessor.name=Full-Board Immersion Device
gt.blockmachines.multimachine.nanochipmodule.boadprocessor.tooltip=Machine Type: §eBoard Processor, NAC Module§r\nModule of the §aNanochip Assembly Complex§7\nProcesses your Board §eCCs§7 by cleaning them in §b'Immersion Fluid'§7\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nWill try to fill its internal tank with provided §b'Immersion Fluids'§7 every second\nThe internal tank has a capacity of §31,000,000L§7 and must be at least half full for the machine to work\nRunning recipes gradually increases fluid impurity, with bigger amounts of fluid taking longer to become impure\nSet an ejection threshold in the GUI to automatically flush the fluid out to be processed, which is §b100%§7 by default\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nThe Impurity percentage §b(y%)§7 affects the module's efficiency:\n§b0%-15%§r - §aEU Discount = 30% - 2 * y%\n§b15%-65%§r - Default behaviour\n§b65%-100%§r - §4Extra EU cost = 2% * y%\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§d§oGotta get'em wet§7\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
