gt.blockmachines.multimachine.spinmatron.tooltip=Machine Type: §eCentrifuge§r\n3 Modes: §dLight§7 | §6Standard§7 | §aHeavy\nOverclocks limited to §fHatch Tier + 1\n§aSupports TecTech Multi-Amp and Laser Hatches!\nThis machine can run recipes regardless of tier, if given enough energy\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nGains §f2§7 Turbine Slots per Structure Tier\n§64§7 Parallels per §fSum of Turbine§7 Tier\nNon-Huge Turbines have reduced effectiveness...\n§a300%§7 Speed\n§b70%§7 EU Usage\nRequires Recipe Tier * §910L/s§7 of §5Kerosene§7 to operate by default\nSupply §5Biocatalyzed Propulsion Fluid§7 instead for a §f1.25x §7Parallel multiplier\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§dLight Mode§7: +§d100%§7 Speed Bonus, Maximum Recipe Tier is §dVoltage Tier - 3\n§6Standard Mode§7: No Changes\n§aHeavy Mode§7: Divides Parallels by §a32§7, Requires T3+ Structure and §5Biocatalyzed Propulsion Fluid\nMultiplies EU Cost by §c16\nSome recipes §c§lrequire§a Heavy Mode\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\n§o§4Maahes guides the way...\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
