gt.blockmachines.multimachine.transcendentplasmamixer.tooltip=Machine Type: §eTranscendent Mixer, TPM§r\nAssisting in all your DTPF needs!\nThis multiblock will run in parallel according to the amount set in the parallel menu\nAll inputs will scale, except time...\nAll EU is deducted from wireless EU networks only\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines\nAdded by: §a§4§l§o§nC§6§l§o§no§a§l§o§nl§3§l§o§ne§5§l§o§nn§r§7
