gt.blockmachines.pipe.bec.block.tooltip=§7Machine Type: §eBEC Conduit§7\n§7Connects several Bose-Einstein Condensate multiblocks together into a network.\n§7Multiblocks must have a §6Bose-Einstein Condensate Hatch§6§7 that connects to a conduit to connect to the network.\n§7Use a §6Bose-Einstein Condensate Maxwell Gate§6§7 to control the flow of condensate.\n§7Can split and turn - multiblocks just have to be connected to link together.\n§7Will only connect to pipes and hatches that match its color.\n§3§lExplosion proof
