gt.blockmachines.sparge.controller.single.name=Sparge Tower Controller
gt.blockmachines.sparge.controller.single.tooltip=Machine Type: §eGas Sparge Tower§r\nRuns gases through depleted molten salts to extract precious fluids\nWorks the same way as the Distillation Tower, but with a fixed height of 8\nFluids are only put out at the correct height\nThe correct height equals the slot number in the NEI recipe\n§7§m-----------------------------------------\nHold §l[LSHIFT]§r§7 to display structure guidelines
